channel.title: Help me?
channel.description: Ok im rather new.....i have a good idea of what to do but what I would like to know is....when i try to log in i cant it says error...server down and i have to make my own server but i ant log into a real account i have to make one up. Is it possible to log in to an actual account on runescpae in a private server and use all the scripts and codes to get my levels up on the real game?? because this is what i thought the whole thing was about but im having trouble working out if this is possible and how.Help me please and please tell me how to get into a actual server to get on an actual runescape account if its possible thankyou mini. :confused:

item.title: Help me?
item.dc:creator: @Javacisnotrecognized _^_
item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

You can’t acess RuneScape from here. They effectively lock us out. What happens is when you put a number in the IP slot, the program looks up that IP and tries to find a server running on it. If there is no active server running on the IP, it returns that error message. If you want to find running servers, go to the server advertisement section for a list of currently running servers. Be sure to read the stickies first though.

item.description:
@lmfaozas wrote:

No its not possible,because all the commands and player controlling is server side,not client side.Even if you would be able to log in with modified client,which probably wont execute your injected commands,you can easilly get busted.
